trans-unit.source: Visual Studio 2015 Tools and Features on not being able to find Visual Studio 2015 in the Start Menu.
trans-unit.target: Visual Studio 2015 Tools and Features on not being able to find Visual Studio 2015 in the Start Menu.

trans-unit.source: I cannot find Visual Studio 2015 in the Start Menu.
trans-unit.target: I cannot find Visual Studio 2015 in the Start Menu.

trans-unit.source: <span class="s1">No, your Visual Studio install is not corrupt.
trans-unit.target: <span class="s1">No, your Visual Studio install is not corrupt.

trans-unit.source: The Visual Studio 2015 application icon has been moved outside of the Visual Studio 2015 folder.
trans-unit.target: The Visual Studio 2015 application icon has been moved outside of the Visual Studio 2015 folder.

trans-unit.source: If you’re running Windows 7, you can find the application at the top of the “All Programs” list grouped with other application icons.
trans-unit.target: If you’re running Windows 7, you can find the application at the top of the “All Programs” list grouped with other application icons.

trans-unit.source: If you are running Windows 8, 8.1 or 10, you can find the application listed under the ‘V’ grouping.
trans-unit.target: If you are running Windows 8, 8.1 or 10, you can find the application listed under the ‘V’ grouping.

trans-unit.source: If you are still unable to find it, use Windows search (press the Windows key, then type “Visual Studio 2015”).
trans-unit.target: If you are still unable to find it, use Windows search (press the Windows key, then type “Visual Studio 2015”).

trans-unit.source: The application icon will no longer be located in the Visual Studio 2015 folder.
trans-unit.target: The application icon will no longer be located in the Visual Studio 2015 folder.

trans-unit.source: <span class="s1">If you are still unable to find Visual Studio after a successful install open your File Explorer and navigate to the following path.
trans-unit.target: <span class="s1">If you are still unable to find Visual Studio after a successful install open your File Explorer and navigate to the following path.

trans-unit.source: C:\Program Files (x86)\Microsoft Visual Studio 14.0\Common7\IDE\devenv.exe and double click on the devenv.exe.
trans-unit.target: C:\Program Files (x86)\Microsoft Visual Studio 14.0\Common7\IDE\devenv.exe and double click on the devenv.exe.

trans-unit.source: If you installed Visual Studio to a drive other than C, go to the location where you installed Visual Studio and navigate to this path Common7\IDE\devenv.exe.
trans-unit.target: If you installed Visual Studio to a drive other than C, go to the location where you installed Visual Studio and navigate to this path Common7\IDE\devenv.exe.
